data.description: Welcome to this timeless gem nestled in the heart of a quiet and established neighborhood! This beautiful home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. With its classic design and modern amenities, this home offers the perfect blend of character and comfort. Step outside into your own backyard haven! The inviting pool is ideal for relaxing on lazy summer days or hosting unforgettable gatherings. Don't miss out on the chance to make this charming beauty your home!
